      "medium": "\n      <p><strong>Big idea.</strong> Studies exchange mechanisms that remain incentive compatible and individually rational under weak informational assumptions.</p>\n      <p><strong>Main result in words.</strong> Robustness substantially constrains exchange and clarifies when efficient trade can survive without detailed type-distribution knowledge.</p>\n      <p><strong>How to read it.</strong> Identify the designer's uncertainty set, the robust performance criterion, and the simple rule that survives the worst-case analysis.</p>\n    ",
